text: Cristina Danielle Valenzuela known professionally as Cristina Vee is an American voice actress. She is known for voicing Sailor Mars in Sailor Moon Crystal, Butterfly in SparkleGlobe Witches, Marinette Dupen Chang in Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir and Lily in Neon Paradise.
